        div.Feature.section
            .info
                | WHAT ARE <br>THE FEATURE
                div.subtitle
                    span
                    | By providing such features, we let you enjoy to code<br>without anything more, try it, you will like it! 
            .sectionContent
                ul
                    li
                        .featureContainer
                            .featureImg
                                img(src="f1.svg", alt="alt")
                            .featureMention
                                .title
                                    | High Scalability
                                .content
                                    | Use docker to seperate database and server, We will hold Nginx to the backward analysis.
                    li
                        .featureContainer
                            .featureImg
                                img(src="f2.svg", alt="alt")
                            .featureMention
                                .title
                                    | High Security
                                .content
                                    | Cover Judge`s core with sandbox, and use docker at the outside to make sure the security.
                            
                    li
                        .featureContainer
                            .featureImg
                                img(src="f3.svg", alt="alt")
                            .featureMention
                                .title
                                    | High Speed
                                .content
                                    | We make sure that each query`s running time will less than 100ms.
                    
        div.Judge.section.reverse
            .info
                | JUDGE INTRO.
                div.subtitle
                    span
                    | simple, but powerful.<br>we bring you to a totally brand new era.
            .sectionContent
                .desktopJudge
                    img(src="desktopJudge.png", alt="desktopJudge")
                .mobileJudge
                    img(src="mobileJudge.png", alt="mobileJudge")
            .cubeContent
                ul
                    - for (var x = 1; x <= 16; x++)
                        li.cube(class='cube' + x)
                            img(src="cube.svg", alt="alt")
        div.Upcoming.section
            .info
                | UP COMING
                div.subtitle
                    span
            .sectionContent
                .mention
                    .FutureContent
                        p
                            | We received a slew of new features in the past few months and is set to get many more in the near future…
