                        span
                            | |
                        span
                            | New UI
                    .FutureBtn.orangeBtn
                        a(href="https://oj.nctu.me/" target="blank")
                            p
                                | Try OJ Today
                .fox
                    img(src="./nctu-fox.png", alt="alt")
